        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="已读书单"><a href="#已读书单" class="headerlink" title="已读书单"></a>已读书单</h3><h4 id="技术"><a href="#技术" class="headerlink" title="技术"></a>技术</h4><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">《网络是怎样链接的》[日] 户根勤《Scrum精髓》Kenneth Rubin《计算机是怎样跑起来的》[日] 矢泽久雄<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h4 id="文学"><a href="#文学" class="headerlink" title="文学"></a>文学</h4><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">《枪炮、病菌与钢铁》[美] 贾雷德·戴蒙德《阿Q正传》鲁迅<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h4 id="理财"><a href="#理财" class="headerlink" title="理财"></a>理财</h4><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">《纳瓦尔宝典》[美] 埃里克·乔根森<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><h4 id="历史"><a href="#历史" class="headerlink" title="历史"></a>历史</h4><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">《挑战古人100天》云葭<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><h4 id="工具"><a href="#工具" class="headerlink" title="工具"></a>工具</h4><h4 id="其他"><a href="#其他" class="headerlink" title="其他"></a>其他</h4><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">《一个广告人的自白》[美] 大卫·奥格威<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
